---
title: Smart Rosemary Double Pork Tenderloin with Apricot-Mustard Vinaigrette, Apples and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Tonight's hearty salad with apples and roasted Brussels sprouts are dressed with an apricot and mustard vinaigrette and topped with rosemary-coated pork tenderloin.  A sprinkling of crunchy seeds completes a hearty salad that's perfect for any time of the year!
